.ascii "0)\x0a    len = grow(0, len, 0x83)\x0a    len = grow(0, len, 0xC0)\x0a   "
.ascii " len = grow(0, len, 0x23)\x0a    \xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb8 len                 #"
